1. *Večeru* smo počeli uz ribu. (We started the evening with fish.)
2. *Večeru* ćemo završiti sa slatkim desertom. (We will end the evening with a sweet dessert.)
3. Često pravim *večere* za moju porodicu. (I often cook dinners for my family.)
4. *Večeru* ćeš imati u 7 časova. (You will have dinner at 7 o'clock.)
5. Ona voli da sprema zanimljive *večere*. (She likes to prepare interesting dinners.)